node.text: Incredibly proud of this partnership with @britishvogue. Executed by an all-female team of creatives, together we “reimagined life in a contemporary Dreamhouse.” Reflecting the fearless individuality of modern, ambitious women, the story writes that they “need not be defined by one role, or a singular definition of beauty and success.” Photographs by Metz & Racine. Styling by PC Williams. Set Design by Penny Mills. Interiors by Jessica Dance. Hair by Lyndell Mansfield. Makeup by Lucy Bridge. The fashions featured are designed by Alexandra Sipa, Alice Khor, Symela Fotiadi and Sohee Park, four recent graduates from London’s leading design schools. #barbie #barbiestyle
